<p align="center">
<br>
<u>
<font face="Arial" size="2">
FTAA - NEGOTIATING GROUP ON COMPETITION POLICY</font></u> </p>
<p align="center"><font face="Arial" size="2">Fourteenth Meeting<br>
<br>
Panama, November 12 - 14, 2001</font></p>
<p align="center">
<u>
<font face="Arial" size="2">
PRESS COMMUNIQU?</font></u></b>
<p>
<ol><li>
<font size="2" face="Arial">The Fourteenth Meeting of the Negotiating Group on 
Competition Policy (NGCP) was held in Panama on November 12-14, 2001. 
Representatives of 21 countries of the Hemisphere were in attendance:<br>
&nbsp;</font><center>
<div align="left">
<table width="391" style="border-collapse: collapse" bordercolor="#111111" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
<tr>
<td align="left" width="141">
